description: This file defines the exported API for the Sys Rro Uint object, including prototype declarations for creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: SysCreateRroUint
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Sys Rro Uint object using provided container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: SysRroUintCreate
methods.description: Constructs a new Sys Rro Uint object instance with specified context handles.

methods.name: SysRroUintRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the Sys Rro Uint object instance.

methods.name: SysRroUintEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrols or registers necessary sub-objects or components within the Sys Rro Uint object.

methods.name: SysRroUintInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Sys Rro Uint object.
